# Inventory API

Allows clients to query for Inventory information. Clients can decide if they want 
to receive all the details for the particular Inventory or just the summary. 

## Inventory [/Inventory]

### Get All Inventory [GET]
Returns all Inventory information

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "item": "1000",
                "name": "Samsung 27 inches Widescreen LED Monitor, Black",                
                "AvailableQuantity": "1048"
            },
