## Inventory Details [/Inventory/details/{item}]

### Get Inventory details [GET]
Returns all details for a specific Inventory

+ Parameters
    + item (number) - Inventory item number.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "item": "1000",
                "name": "Samsung 27 inches Widescreen LED Monitor, Black",                
                "AvailableQuantity": "1048"
            }
        ]


## Inventory Summary [/Inventory/summary/{item}]

### Get Inventory Summary [GET]
Returns only a summary of the Inventory (product name and Available Quantity / QOH)).

+ Parameters
    + item (number) - Inventory item number.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "item": "1000",
                "name": "Samsung 27 inches Widescreen LED Monitor, Black",                
                "AvailableQuantity": "1048"
            }
        ]